<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 06:16:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>2024年民主将走向何方？特朗普可能拥有最终决定权</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/where-is-democracy-headed-2024-trump-may-have-final-word-2023-12-18/</link><description>俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京 (Vladimir Putin) 看来将继续掌权至少到 2030 年；印度的纳伦德拉·莫迪 (Narendra Modi) 似乎肯定会将其统治延长至 2029 年；尽管被指控颠覆美国民主，唐纳德·特朗普仍可能重返白宫。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 06:08:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/where-is-democracy-headed-2024-trump-may-have-final-word-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国与朝鲜在导弹发射期间举行高层会晤</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-north-korea-hold-high-level-meeting-amid-missile-launches-2023-12-18/</link><description>中国外交部长王毅周一在北京与朝鲜副外长举行高层会谈，恰逢平壤发射了一枚能够到达美国任何地方的导弹。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 06:01:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-north-korea-hold-high-level-meeting-amid-missile-launches-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：市场在日本央行“会或不会”上发挥作用</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2023-12-18/</link><description>韦恩·科尔 (Wayne Cole) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 05:32:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>中国首艘超深水钻井船将进行海试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-conduct-sea-trials-its-first-ultra-deepwater-drilling-ship-2023-12-18/</link><description>中国将于周五对其第一艘海洋研究钻探船进行海上试验，该船能够在超过10,000米（32,800英尺）的深度进行钻探，这是增强中国深海石油和天然气勘探能力的关键一步。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 05:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-conduct-sea-trials-its-first-ultra-deepwater-drilling-ship-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>由于限制措施不断加强，亚洲化肥买家不再关注主要出口国中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asian-fertiliser-buyers-turn-away-key-exporter-china-amid-growing-curbs-2023-12-18/</link><description>买家和分析师表示，亚洲化肥买家正在寻找中国供应的替代品，因为他们担心，在为保护国内市场而限制发货后，中国这个世界最大的出口国已成为一个越来越不可靠的供应商。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 04:37:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/asian-fertiliser-buyers-turn-away-key-exporter-china-amid-growing-curbs-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>官员称2024年中国经济状况将改善</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economic-conditions-improve-2024-officials-2023-12-18/</link><description>官方媒体援引中共中央财经办公室官员的话称，预计2024年中国经济将面临更多有利条件、机遇多于挑战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 02:43:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-economic-conditions-improve-2024-officials-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>花旗集团中国投资银行计划因数据法而推迟 - 彭博新闻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-china-investment-bank-plans-delayed-by-data-law-bloomberg-news-2023-12-18/</link><description>据彭博社周一报道，花旗集团在中国设立全资证券业务的计划比预期要长，因为该银行需要更多时间来遵守中国的数据法。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 01:38:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/citigroup-china-investment-bank-plans-delayed-by-data-law-bloomberg-news-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报告更多疑似中国气象气球穿越台湾海峡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-detected-two-chinese-balloons-crossing-taiwan-strait-sunday-defence-2023-12-18/</link><description>台湾国防部周一表示，两个疑似中国气象气球周日飞越敏感的台湾海峡，但仍停留在台湾北部，这是台北本月第二次报告它们在附近。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 01:11:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-detected-two-chinese-balloons-crossing-taiwan-strait-sunday-defence-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>香港具有里程碑意义的黎智英安全审判开庭，安保严密</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/security-tight-ahead-landmark-trial-leading-hong-kong-democrat-2023-12-18/</link><description>对中国主要批评者黎智英的一次具有里程碑意义的国家安全审判周一在戒备森严的情况下在香港开庭，这位亲民主活动人士对他与包括美国在内的外国势力勾结的指控进行了斗争。</description><pubDate>Mon, 18 Dec 2023 00:58:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/security-tight-ahead-landmark-trial-leading-hong-kong-democrat-2023-12-18/</guid></item><item><title>香港奢侈品零售商调整以应对高消费中国游客的下降</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hong-kong-luxury-retailers-adjusting-drop-high-spending-chinese-tourists-2023-12-17/</link><description>香港的奢侈品零售商正在适应来香港旅游的中国富裕购物者的减少，以及游客涌向时尚地区那些在 Instagram 上令人垂涎的景点的趋势，而不是花钱购买昂贵的品牌装备。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 23:06:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hong-kong-luxury-retailers-adjusting-drop-high-spending-chinese-tourists-2023-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国公司希望在马来西亚组装高端芯片</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-look-malaysia-assembly-high-end-chips-sources-say-2023-12-17/</link><description>消息人士称，越来越多的中国半导体设计公司正在利用马来西亚公司来组装部分高端芯片，热衷于对冲美国扩大对中国芯片行业制裁的风险。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 23:03:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinese-firms-look-malaysia-assembly-high-end-chips-sources-say-2023-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>香港审判开始之际，英国呼吁释放黎智英</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/britain-calls-jimmy-lais-release-hong-kong-trial-begins-2023-12-17/</link><description>英国呼吁香港在对这位主要中国批评者和媒体大亨进行审判之前释放黎智英，罪名是他与包括美国在内的外国势力勾结。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 22:32:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/britain-calls-jimmy-lais-release-hong-kong-trial-begins-2023-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国发布非银行支付机构监督管理办法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-publishes-rules-supervising-managing-non-bank-payment-firms-2023-12-17/</link><description>由国务院总理李强领导的中国国务院周日发布了非银行支付机构监督管理规定，该规定将于 5 月 1 日起施行。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 08:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-publishes-rules-supervising-managing-non-bank-payment-firms-2023-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>英国国家电网因网络安全担忧而放弃中国供应商 - FT</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/britains-national-grid-drops-china-based-supplier-over-cyber-security-fears-ft-2023-12-17/</link><description>据英国《金融时报》周日报道，出于对网络安全的担忧，英国国家电网已开始从输电网络中移除由中国支持的南瑞科技旗下子公司提供的组件。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 06:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/britains-national-grid-drops-china-based-supplier-over-cyber-security-fears-ft-2023-12-17/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾欲在南海启动新能源勘探项目</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-says-tensions-south-china-sea-have-increased-2023-12-17/</link><description>菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯表示，菲律宾正在努力解决南海的“勘探问题”，以便在资源丰富的水道上启动新的能源勘探项目，以满足菲律宾的能源需求。</description><pubDate>Sun, 17 Dec 2023 03:05:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-marcos-says-tensions-south-china-sea-have-increased-2023-12-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>